 UNEs). We argue that neither of\nthese approaches is likely to achieve the desired result for FTTH, given the\ncurrent state of flux in emerging FTTH technology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2001 20:32:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Oct 2001 04:50:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
